  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Dykstra‚Äôs alternating projection algorithm <label for="2" class="margin-toggle sidenote-number"></label><input type="checkbox" id="2" class="margin-toggle" /><span class="sidenote">Dykstra, R. L. (1983). An algorithm for restricted least squares regression. J. Amer. Statist. Assoc., 78(384):837-842. </span></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Proximal point algorithm applied to the dual</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Numerous applications in statistics and machine learning: lasso, gen. lasso, graphical lasso, (overlapping) group lasso, ‚Ä¶
